649
00:40:05,904 --> 00:40:07,488
Dahil 'yan sa dami ng ulan ngayong tag-init.

650
00:40:07,655 --> 00:40:09,073
Ayos lang. Sinuri ko na lahat.

651
00:40:09,157 --> 00:40:12,243
